org.freedesktop.wayland.util

Class InterfaceMeta

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.freedesktop.wayland.util.InterfaceMeta
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasNative<wl_interface>

    public class InterfaceMeta
extends java.lang.Object
implements HasNative<wl_interface>
    Wrapper class for any Java type to get or create a native wayland interface for use with the native wayland library. To get a native wayland interface for a given Java type, use get(Class).
